1. SETUP
Make sure you have:
woocommerce (that includes everything from 'wp-content/plugins/woocommerce/templates')
src/js/woocommerce
src/scss/woocommerce.scss
src/scss/woocommerce-custom.scss
woocommerce.php
woocommerce-functions.php

And in functions.php:
require_once get_template_directory() . '/woocommerce-functions.php';

2. CUSTOMIZE WOOCOMMERCE TEMPLATES

SINGLE PRODUCT
Template: content-single-product.php
Note 1: do_action('woocommerce_single_product_summary') is necessary in order to load the default JS/jQuery for variable products options.
Note 2: do_action('woocommerce_before_single_product_summary') is necessary in order to load the default JS/jQuery for product gallery.

SINGLE PRODUCT FEATURED IMAGE
Template: single-product/product-image.php
Note:  No lightbox and not clickable featured image if no gallery

SINGLE PRODUCT VARIATION INPUT 
Template: single-product/add-to-cart/variable.php
Note: Remove label and Custom placeholder

QUANTITY
Template: global/quantity-input.php
Note: Once, we modify the template for visual reasons, we use our own JS for the quantity functionality
